HEADWORD: Deathless
<hw>Death"less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not subject to death,
destruction, or extinction; immortal; undying; imperishable; <as>as,
<ex>deathless</ex> beings; <ex>deathless</ex> fame.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

